Authorization tokens are issued and returned when a user registers. A registered user can also retrieve their token with the following request:  Request :  POST   api-token-auth/  Parameters:     Name  Type  Description      username  string  The user's username    password  string  The user's password     Response :  { 
    "token" : "9944b09199c62bcf9418ad846dd0e4bbdfc6ee4b" 
